The paper proposes a deep learning-based computer aided diagnosis system for the classification of Intraductal Papillary Mucinous Neoplasms (IPMN) using multi-modal MRI. This work involves image processing, computer vision, and machine learning techniques, which are commonly associated with the computer science sub-categories of computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
